   geo-political economic culture. These goals include Belarus' desire to
   reduce its dependence on Russian gas and oil, upgrade and diversify its
   economy, strengthen its integration with Eurasia and find new partners,
   by attracting Chinese and other foreign direct investment in the context
   of China's Going Out and Belt and Road Initiative (BRI). An analysis of
