   DN of PRISM and AVNIR-2. The reflectance of AVNIR-2 is calculated from
   calculated DN values. UPDM method is applied to the set of re-calculated
   reflectance. Using the coefficients of UPDM and vegetation index,
   evergreen forest and deciduous forest were classified using two seasonal
   data. These results are compared with forest resource information. The
   tendency was agree with each other, although detailed validation is
