   Freemium (Free + Premium), revenue sharing among the chain of service
   providers, subsidized billing by USOF (Universal Service Obligation
   Funds). Finally, the white paper presents a 10-year roadmap starting
   from the current state to 3 years, 5 years and 10 years.},
